Name: Code Tracer
About the game: Code Tracer is a simple puzzle game. You only have to cut codes, but be careful about time and electricity. The tension of playing with a limited amount of time It's a tense game that requires you to make quick and appropriate movements within a limited amount of time. Medal system You can earn medals according to your score, and you can unlock stages with medals. The boss stage is not a straightforward one
